  "details": "Apache Avro is a data serialization system.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nA vulnerability in the .NET SDK of Apache Avro allows an attacker to allocate excessive resources, potentially causing a denial-of-service attack. This issue affects .NET applications using Apache Avro version 1.10.2 and prior versions. Users should update to version 1.11.0 which addresses this issue.(CVE-2021-43045)",
